'''心病毒屬'''（'''{{lang|en|Cardiovirus}}'''），又称为'''心脏病毒属'''，是[[微小核醣核酸病毒科|微小核醣核酸病毒科]]裡的一[[屬|屬]]，脊椎動物是這類病毒的天然宿主<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|last=Blinkova|first=Olga|last2=Kapoor|first2=Amit|last3=Victoria|first3=Joseph|last4=Jones|first4=Morris|last5=Wolfe|first5=Nathan|last6=Naeem|first6=Asif|last7=Shaukat|first7=Shahzad|last8=Sharif|first8=Salmaan|last9=Alam|first9=Muhammad Masroor|last10=Angez|first10=Mehar|last11=Zaidi|first11=Sohail|date=2009-05-01|title=Cardioviruses Are Genetically Diverse and Cause Common Enteric Infections in South Asian Children|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-virology_2009-05_83_9/page/4631|journal=Journal of Virology|language=en|volume=83|issue=9|pages=4631–4641|doi=10.1128/JVI.02085-08|issn=0022-538X|pmid=19193786|pmc=2668475}}</ref>，下含甲型心病毒至己型心病毒6个物种<ref name=":1" /><ref name=ViralZone>{{cite web|title=Viral Zone|url=http://viralzone.expasy.org/all_by_species/99.html|publisher=ExPASy|accessdate=15 June 2015|archive-date=2017-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170221131613/http://viralzone.expasy.org/all_by_species/99.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ICTV>{{cite web|url=https://talk.ictvonline.org/taxonomy/|title=Virus Taxonomy: 2019 Release|last=|first=|date=|website=talk.ictvonline.org|publisher=International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses|access-date=7 May 2020|quote=|archive-date=2020-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320103754/https://talk.ictvonline.org/taxonomy|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最初于1981年得到培养分离。

心病毒属的病毒都是单链[[RNA病毒|RNA病毒]]、无[[病毒包膜|病毒包膜]]包膜包裹，直径约30纳米、基因组长约7.8千碱基<ref name="ViralZone" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|last=Himeda|first=Toshiki|last2=Ohara|first2=Yoshiro|date=February 2012|title=Saffold Virus, a Novel Human Cardiovirus with Unknown Pathogenicity|journal=Journal of Virology|volume=86|issue=3|pages=1292–1296|doi=10.1128/JVI.06087-11|issn=0022-538X|pmc=3264344|pmid=22114344}}</ref>。

